				<ul>
					<li>Improved onboarding flow</li>
					<li>Improments in the Watch-Only login view</li>
					<li>Reinstate 2FA reset notification and request/cancel options</li>
					<li>Add general section in app settings</li>
					<li>Update GDK to 0.70.3</li>
				</ul>
			<p>Fixed</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Crash on login when Ledger device is idle</li>
